     H            Y.
     F** EDSR02 ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY -  SAVE GDGPP10 TO GDGPP10S      *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)   2023.10.02                    *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     FGDGPP10 IF  E                    DISK
     FGDGPP10SO   E                    DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140D#TIME
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $PGM   10
      *
      * INITIAL SETTING
     C                     TIME           D#TIME
      *
      * SAVE GDGPP10 --------------------------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ GDGPP10                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     IBCRHZ
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       IBCRTM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     IBCRME
     C                     MOVEL$PGM      IBCRPG
     C                     WRITEGDGPP10R
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
